title: Photography for Beginners - Issue 11 2012 (.PDF)
description: Photography for Beginners magazine is accessible, inspirational and loaded with practical guides. Learn to shoot better images with the beginners techniques, around the mode dial features and big projects. Perfect your photos with image editing workshops using Photoshop, Paint Shop Pro, iPhoto, GIMP, the iPad and android apps. Discover the best sites to share your photos on. Every issue of Photography for Beginners addresses all this, and more!
